item.title: Pneumonia X-ray
item.description: Link to Github repository Chest x-ray image of normal lungsThis project involves building a deep neural network that trains on a large dataset for classification on a non-trivial task. In this case, the task is using x-ray images of patients to classify whether or not they have pneumonia. The Dataset The dataset originates from Kermany et al. on Mendeley. The particular subset used for this project is sourced via Kaggle.
